@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">@ViewData["Title"] - <span class="text-primary">BuzzAir</span></h2>

    <div class="card shadow-sm p-4 border-0">
        <p>
            At <strong>BuzzAir</strong>, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting the personal information you share with us. This policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our website and services.
        </p>

        <h4 class="mt-4 text-primary">1. Information We Collect</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Personal Identification Information (e.g., name, email address, phone number, passport details)</li>
            <li>Payment Information (processed securely via trusted third-party providers)</li>
            <li>Travel Preferences and History</li>
            <li>Technical Data (IP address, browser type, device information)</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="mt-4 text-primary">2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Process flight bookings and issue tickets</li>
            <li>Send you booking confirmations and updates</li>
            <li>Offer personalized promotions and travel recommendations</li>
            <li>Enhance and improve our website functionality and customer experience</li>
            <li>Comply with legal obligations (e.g., customs and immigration requirements)</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="mt-4 text-primary">3. Sharing Your Information</h4>
        <p>
            BuzzAir does <strong>not</strong> sell your personal data. However, we may share your information with:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Partner airlines and travel agencies to complete your booking</li>
            <li>Payment processors and fraud detection services</li>
            <li>Government authorities when legally required</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="mt-4 text-primary">4. Data Security</h4>
        <p>
            We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information. All sensitive data is encrypted and stored securely. Only authorized personnel have access to your personal information.
        </p>

        <h4 class="mt-4 text-primary">5. Cookies & Tracking</h4>
        <p>
            Our website uses cookies to improve your browsing experience and analyze site traffic. You can manage your cookie preferences in your browser settings.
        </p>

        <h4 class="mt-4 text-primary">6. Your Rights</h4>
        <p>
            You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. You may also request that we restrict or stop processing your data under certain circumstances. To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@buzzair.com">privacy@buzzair.com</a>.
        </p>

        <h4 class="mt-4 text-primary">7. Changes to This Policy</h4>
        <p>
            BuzzAir may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in legal requirements or our services. All updates will be posted on this page.
        </p>

        <h4 class="mt-4 text-primary">8. Contact Us</h4>
        <address class="mb-4">
            BuzzAir Privacy Office<br />
            123 Skyway Blvd<br />
            Terminal 5, London Heathrow Airport<br />
            London, UK<br />
            <strong>Phone (UK):</strong> +44 555 0123 4567<br />
            <strong>Phone (US):</strong> +1 (555) 456-7890<br />
            <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@buzzair.com">privacy@buzzair.com</a>
        </address>

        <p class="text-muted"><em>Last updated: May 2025</em></p>
    </div>
</div>
